{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"64e52880ea","title":"大字报——我们也来接一棒","origin":"《南开大学右派反动言论选集》（天津：南开大学社会主义思想教育教研室，1957年9月）。","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"12336ff0d1","index":0,"year":1957,"month":5,"day":null,"articleId":"64e52880ea"}],"tags":[{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"CCRD-fanyou","name":"中国反右运动数据库","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":""}],"authors":[{"id":"54de09977c","name":"朱元镇"},{"id":"66d3fb53e8","name":"魏力仁"},{"id":"f2840d39f9","name":"南开大学"}]},"publication_details":{"CCRD-fanyou":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"137bc4f6bf","type":"title","text":"大字报——我们也来接一棒","index":0,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"64e52880ea"},{"id":"5a1bb59584","type":"authors","text":"南开大学朱元镇魏力仁","index":1,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"64e52880ea"},{"id":"59d666896c","type":"subtitle","text":"[朱元镇、魏力仁：南开大学数学系学生]","index":2,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"64e52880ea"},{"id":"6444183a87","type":"paragraph","text":"国家兴亡  匹夫有责","index":3,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"64e52880ea"},{"id":"3bad671ea1","type":"paragraph","text":"肃清三害  人人动手","index":4,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"64e52880ea"},{"id":"3a53561d6f","type":"paragraph","text":"（一）大学里在保证党的领导下，改变党委决定一切、包办一切、充分发挥教授治校、民主办校精神。","index":5,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"64e52880ea"},{"id":"3685ac7540","type":"paragraph","text":"（二）反对一些吹、拍、奉迎、阿谀奉承媚上骄下的奴才、小人当道。","index":6,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"64e52880ea"},{"id":"c99bdbe705","type":"paragraph","text":"（三）反对培养四平八稳、培养木偶尾巴的优秀生制度。","index":7,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"64e52880ea"},{"id":"64c4919b2f","type":"paragraph","text":"（四）反对所谓政治条件，把同学分成九等六级。","index":8,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"64e52880ea"},{"id":"8cd0b7e947","type":"paragraph","text":"（五）留学生要通过考试选拔，反对政府脱离实际生活状况，为留学生讲排场，摆架子。（目前政府给留学生每人每月要花七百多元）。","index":9,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"64e52880ea"},{"id":"d01682bad7","type":"paragraph","text":"（六）要求人事制度公开，要求对学生的鉴定公开。要求毕业生分配工作公开，我们不是“木头”，不能随少数人的喜怒哀乐来支配。","index":10,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"64e52880ea"},{"id":"7d486ec8f3","type":"paragraph","text":"（七）公开冤枉被斗的人，公开恢复名誉和道歉。","index":11,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"64e52880ea"},{"id":"a1f63cd5d6","type":"paragraph","text":"（八）反对人民南开成为官僚主义的遮羞布。","index":12,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"64e52880ea"},{"id":"b148b97034","type":"paragraph","text":"（九）共产党员、共青团员到群众中来一起清除三害。","index":13,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"64e52880ea"},{"id":"c069411142","type":"paragraph","text":"数三（三）七人","index":14,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"64e52880ea"},{"id":"51ebfe05f3","type":"paragraph","text":"魏力仁 朱元镇 刘文辅 卢德思 陈远翚 王文 李时吉（起草人朱元镇 魏力仁）","index":15,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"64e52880ea"}],"page":{"id":"d9e2cfc2b2","publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"64e52880ea","start":0,"end":0}}}},"__N_SSG":true}